dc_title_s: [Geological Survey of England and Wales : one inch to the mile map. New Series.] Tavistock, drift, sheet 337
dc_description_s: Geological Survey of Great Britain (England and Wales) Great Britain. Ordnance Survey. Sheet 337 drift. North Decimal Degree 50.6500. South Decimal Degree 50.4833.
